page.title: 16PLANTS IN A CORNISH HEDGE
page.content: {PLANT LIST }16th July 1985 Foxglove Elm Tufted Vetch Bindweed Yorkshirefog Hedge Bindweed Red Campion Common Vetch Meadow foxtail Common Field Blackthorn Speedwort Lymegrass Pineapple Mayweed Meadow Thistle Groundsel Hawthorn Common Ragwort Brambles Goosegrass Nettle Elderberry bush Common Bent Grass Cut-leaved Cranes- Gorse bill Hogweed Tall Fescue Cow Parsley Prickly Sow Thistle Creeping thistle Hart's Tongue Common Thistle Soft Brome Timothy Barley Ivy {THESE PLANTS WERE FOUND Dandelion {OVER A 30m LENGTH OF Catsear {HEDGE NEAR MULLION.}
